703.jpg\" alt=\"“... suddenly I found that I had no rider... Blind terror drove me on, with my flying stirrups... I reach the kneeling riflemen first” – DG Smith’s (US) illustration of the First Charge in War Horse\" width=\"703\" height=\"1000\" class=\"gu-image\" /> <figcaption> <span class=\"element-image__caption\"><strong>DG Smith (US)</strong><br>“… suddenly I found that I had no rider … Blind terror drove me on, with my flying stirrups … I reach the kneeling riflemen first.” – Chapter six</span> <span class=\"element-image__credit\">Illustration: DG Smith</span> </figcaption> </figure>  <figure class=\"element element-image\" data-media-id=\"8d858367967a6ee4941470cad76cdfa7c64f81eb\"> <img src=\"http://media.guim.co.uk/8d858367967a6ee4941470cad76cdfa7c64f81eb/0_0_886_1258/704.jpg\" alt=\"‘Suddenly I found I had no rider’ ... Nathan Aardvark (UK) illustration for competition to win commission to illustrate Folio Society edition of Michael Morpurgo’s War Horse\" width=\"704\" height=\"1000\" class=\"gu-image\" /> <figcaption> <span class=\"element-image__caption\"><strong>Nathan Aardvark (UK)</strong><br>‘Suddenly I found I had no rider.’ – Chapter six</span> <span class=\"element-image__credit\">Illustration: Nathan Aardvark</span> </figcaption> </figure>  <figure class=\"element element-image\" data-media-id=\"8704779530cc28042683a74be7211ccb59a3a4ba\"> <img src=\"http://media.guim.co.uk/8704779530cc28042683a74be7211ccb59a3a4ba/0_0_886_1222/725.jpg\" alt=\"“I ran on until I found myself alone...It had all been so quick and deadly.” - Holly Francis (UK)\" width=\"725\" height=\"1000\" class=\"gu-image\" /> <figcaption> <span class=\"element-image__caption\"><strong>Holly Francis (UK)</strong><br>‘I ran on until I found myself alone … It had all been so quick and deadly.’ – Chapter six</span> <span class=\"element-image__credit\">Illustration: Holly Francis</span> </figcaption> </figure>  <figure class=\"element element-image\" data-media-id=\"3c6992163e88e5c97