 dawn behind it, a great grey lumbering monster that belched out smoke from behind it as it rocked down the hillside towards me” Divya Scialo (UK)\" width=\"695\" height=\"1000\" class=\"gu-image\" /> <figcaption> <span class=\"element-image__caption\"><strong>Divya Scialo (UK)</strong><br>‘Although I didn’t know it as such, the first tank I ever saw came over the rise of the hill with the cold light of dawn behind it, a great grey lumbering monster that belched out smoke from behind it as it rocked down the hillside towards me.’ – Chapter fifteen</span> <span class=\"element-image__credit\">Illustration: Divya Scialo</span> </figcaption> </figure>  <figure class=\"element element-image\" data-media-id=\"21e25ea05a039aaad0554e6771e1e994f4ef1724\"> <img src=\"http://media.guim.co.uk/21e25ea05a039aaad0554e6771e1e994f4ef1724/0_0_886_1258/704.jpg\" alt=\"“... the thunder and lightning of the bombardment was so terrible in its intensity, turning the deep black of night into unnatural day...” Fi Smart (UK)\" width=\"704\" height=\"1000\" class=\"gu-image\" /> <figcaption> <span class=\"element-image__caption\"><strong>Fi Smart (UK)</strong><br>‘ … the thunder and lightning of the bombardment was so terrible in its intensity, turning the deep black of night into unnatural day… ’ - Chapter fifteen</span> <span class=\"element-image__credit\">Illustration: Fi Smart</span> </figcaption> </figure>  <figure class=\"element element-image\" data-media-id=\"1ca8a61bfb1c746c29ea1f7ec16f61345f27ba38\"> <img src=\"http://media.guim.co.uk/1ca8a61bfb1c746c29ea1f7ec16f61345f27ba38/0_0_886_1267/699.jpg\" alt=\"“Within minutes the mist began to clear away” - Alan Marks (UK)\" width=\"699\" height=\"1000\" class=\"gu-image\" /> <figcaption> <span class=\"element-image__caption\"><strong>Alan Marks (UK)</strong><br>‘Within minutes the mist began to clear away.’ – Chapter fifteen</span> <span class=\"element-image__credit\">Illustration: Alan Marks</span> </figcaption> </figure>  <figure cla